    "DockDoor Pro has no telemetry, analytics, or behavior tracking. Window and app state stays on your Mac. Location is only used for WeatherKit when you enable local weather. Network access is used for activation checks, updates, and features you choose to use such as WeatherKit and lyrics lookup." : {
